                    </div>
                    <span>Colin Powell gives us his strategies for success in this wonderful book.  I am a CEO of a Fortune 500 company who has struggled with some of these issues over the years.  This book helped me to understand that I am not alone and that some issues, although unspoken, are shared by all in leadership roles.</span>
                  
              
